---
title: American BBQ Beef Rissoles with Kumara Fries & Tomato Salad
description: These rissoles are bursting with the tried and true flavour of our All-American spice blend and tangy BBQ sauce. On the side, we've got a bright salad and wholesome oven-baked kumara fries for a splendid finish.
